                     <interp inst="t18510512-1039-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> stealing 2 shawls, and other goods, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 14<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18510512-name-22" type="victimName">
