                        <interp inst="t18510512-name-25" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM HEATH</persName>
                  </hi>. I sell greens. I know the prisoner by sight—he came to my place, 31, Queen-street, and brought these two shawls—I bought them of him—I afterwards gave them to the prosecutor.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
