                  </hi>. I am a sawyer. On Sunday evening, 6th April, between eight and nine o'clock, I saw the prisoner at the Fox and Hounds, at Chelsea—he offered this handkerchief for sale—I bought it of him, and gave it up to the prosecutor.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18510512-name-27" type="witnessName">
